A cold drink would be fine. Thank you.

767
01:09:18,654 --> 01:09:21,739
Mr. Hammersmith, your office said
I might find you at home.

768
01:09:21,949 --> 01:09:23,616
Hope I'm not troubling you.

769
01:09:24,285 --> 01:09:26,411
