770
01:09:26,579 --> 01:09:30,623
Paul Edgecomb. I'm E Block supervisor
up on Cold Mountain.

771
01:09:31,834 --> 01:09:33,209
The Green Mile.

772
01:09:33,419 --> 01:09:36,546
Yeah, I've heard of it.
