785
01:10:14,460 --> 01:10:17,212
- Thank you, missus.
- My pleasure.

786
01:10:18,088 --> 01:10:21,382
Kids! Lunch is about ready.
Y'all come on up.

787
01:10:21,634 --> 01:10:22,926
<font color="#804040">TOGETHER</font>: Coming, Mama!

788
01:10:23,135 --> 01:10:26,262
