814
01:11:48,554 --> 01:11:51,139
Everyone is entitled to a defense.

815
01:11:51,557 --> 01:11:53,182
<font color="#804040">MRS. HAMMERSMITH</font>: Kids!
Lunch!

816
01:11:53,392 --> 01:11:54,684
